         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Hillston ¶  12.8.82 ¶ Baron ¶  ¶ The principal grass here is that of which I enclose a specimen[.] It does not however stand the summer well for after it seeds early in November or at latest in the be...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">82.08.12a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From A. N. Grant</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M113, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS found with a specimen of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Austrodanthonia caespitosa</seg> (MEL 2125680).</p>
               </note>Hillston<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>NSW.</p>
               </note> 12.8.82</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The principal grass here is that of which I enclose a specimen[.] It does not however stand the summer well for after it seeds early in November or at latest in the beginning of December it is gone until the autumn rains unless the summer is a wet one</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>There is an acacia here in leaf and appearance like but electing for a hibitat the driest red clays and arid sandhills. It is not so tall by any means as acicia<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">sic<seg style="font-weight: bold; ">.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> decurrens and is very prolific in Gum. It is a very pretty plant and many of them much more beautiful than others<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See also A. N. Grant to M, 4 September 1882 (in this edition as 82-09-04a).</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear Baron</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Yours faithfully &amp; respectfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>A. N. Grant</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">The Baron Von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Acacia%20decurrens">Acacia decurrens</name>
            </p>
